title: Six James Bond waxworks unveiled at Madame Tussauds [Photos]
text:
Six James Bond waxworks unveiled at Madame Tussauds First posted: Thursday, October 22, 2015 11:17 AM EDT Six James Bond waxworks unveiled at Madame Tussauds Previous Next 
Madame Tussauds London revealed wax figures of all six James Bonds, with five completely new wax 007s joining the existing figure of Daniel Craig. To coincide with the release of SPECTRE, the line-up of Sean Connery, George Lazenby, Roger Moore, Timothy Dalton, Pierce Brosnan and Daniel Craig will appear at the legendary London attraction for six weeks, before embarking on a tour of Madame Tussauds locations worldwide on Dec. 1. (WENN.com) Supplied by WENN.com
